<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>C-TOKEN CSM++ v4.0 — Enterprise Semantic Compression Engine</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Adaptive semantic compression with entropy-based token intelligence. 50k+ ops/sec, <5ms latency. The next infrastructure layer for AI systems.">
    
    <!-- Tailwind CSS -->
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    
    <!-- Lucide Icons -->
    <script src="https://unpkg.com/lucide@latest"></script>
    
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        html {
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
        }

        :root {
            --color-bg-dark: #0f0f23;
            --color-bg-darker: #0a0a18;
            --color-primary: #3b82f6;
            --color-purple: #a855f7;
            --color-pink: #ec4899;
            --color-text-primary: #f8fafc;
            --color-text-secondary: #94a3b8;
            --color-border: #1e293b;
            --spacing-xs: 0.5rem;
            --spacing-sm: 1rem;
            --spacing-md: 1.5rem;
            --spacing-lg: 2rem;
            --spacing-xl: 3rem;
            --spacing-2xl: 4rem;
        }

        body {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-bg-dark) 0%, #1a1a3e 50%, #15213e 100%);
            color: var(--color-text-secondary);
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', 'Roboto', 'Oxygen', 'Ubuntu', 'Cantarell', sans-serif;
            position: relative;
            overflow-x: hidden;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        @keyframes float {
            0%, 100% { transform: translate(0, 0) scale(1); }
            50% { transform: translate(30px, -30px) scale(1.05); }
        }

        @keyframes fadeInUp {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(30px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        @keyframes slideIn {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateX(-20px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateX(0);
            }
        }

        @keyframes glow-pulse {
            0%, 100% { box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.3); }
            50% { box-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.6); }
        }

        @keyframes shimmer {
            0%, 100% { opacity: 0.5; }
            50% { opacity: 1; }
        }

        @keyframes bar-rise {
            from { transform: scaleY(0); }
            to { transform: scaleY(1); }
        }

        @keyframes slideUp {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(40px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        @keyframes breathe {
            0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
            50% { opacity: 0.8; }
        }

        .fade-in-up {
            animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease-out;
        }

        .slide-in {
            animation: slideIn 0.8s ease-out;
        }

        .glow-button {
            animation: glow-pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        .shimmer-text {
            animation: shimmer 3s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        .gradient-text {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-primary) 0%, var(--color-purple) 50%, var(--color-pink) 100%);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
        }

        .glass {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        }

        .glass-hover {
            transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
        }

        .glass-hover:hover {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
            border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
            transform: translateY(-4px);
        }

        .chart-bar {
            animation: bar-rise 0.8s ease-out backwards;
        }

        .chart-bar:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: 0s; }
        .chart-bar:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.1s; }
        .chart-bar:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 0.2s; }

        .hero-text {
            font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 8vw, 5rem);
            font-weight: 800;
            letter-spacing: -2px;
            line-height: 1.1;
        }

        .subtitle-text {
            font-size: clamp(1.125rem, 4vw, 1.5rem);
            font-weight: 500;
            color: var(--color-text-secondary);
        }

        .feature-card {
            transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
            border-radius: 12px;
        }

        .feature-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-12px);
            box-shadow: 0 24px 48px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.15);
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
            border-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.3);
        }

        .metric-item {
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .metric-item:hover {
            transform: scale(1.03);
        }

        .code-block {
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
            border: 1px solid rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.2);
            border-radius: 12px;
            font-family: 'Monaco', 'Menlo', 'Ubuntu Mono', monospace;
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .token-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
            background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.15);
            border: 1px solid rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.3);
            border-radius: 9999px;
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #93c5fd;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .content-wrapper {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 10;
        }

        .section-padding {
            padding: 4rem 2rem;
        }

        .nav-bar {
            height: 5rem;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            padding: 0 2rem;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 100;
        }

        .nav-logo {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-primary), var(--color-pink));
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        }

        .btn {
            padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.25s ease;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            letter-spacing: 0.3px;
        }

        .btn-primary {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-primary), var(--color-purple));
            color: white;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.3);
        }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 12px 24px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.4);
        }

        .btn-secondary {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            color: white;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
        }

        .btn-secondary:hover {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
            border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
        }

        .stat-box {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
            border-radius: 12px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .stat-box:hover {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
            border-color: var(--color-primary);
        }

        .stat-value {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-primary), var(--color-pink));
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .stat-label {
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            color: var(--color-text-secondary);
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .section-padding {
                padding: 3rem 1rem;
            }
            .hero-text {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }
            .nav-bar {
                padding: 0 1rem;
            }
        }

        /* Enhanced form inputs */
        input, textarea, button {
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        input:focus, textarea:focus {
            outline: none;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.4);
            border-color: var(--color-primary);
        }

        button:active {
            transform: scale(0.98);
        }

        /* Scrollbar styling */
        ::-webkit-scrollbar {
            width: 8px;
        }

        ::-webkit-scrollbar-track {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        }

        ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {
            background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.3);
            border-radius: 4px;
        }

        ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:hover {
            background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5);
        }

        /* Better link styling */
        a {
            color: var(--color-primary);
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
        }

        a:hover {
            color: var(--color-pink);
        }

        /* Typography improvements */
        h1, h2, h3, h4, h5, h6 {
            color: var(--color-text-primary);
            line-height: 1.2;
        }

        h2 {
            font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        h3 {
            font-size: clamp(1.25rem, 3vw, 1.875rem);
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
        }

        p {
            color: var(--color-text-secondary);
        }

        /* Enhanced badge styles */
        .badge {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
            padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
            background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.1);
            border: 1px solid rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.3);
            border-radius: 9999px;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #93c5fd;
        }

        .badge-success {
            background: rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.1);
            border-color: rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.3);
            color: #86efac;
        }

        .badge-warning {
            background: rgba(251, 191, 36, 0.1);
            border-color: rgba(251, 191, 36, 0.3);
            color: #fcd34d;
        }

        .badge-danger {
            background: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.1);
            border-color: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.3);
            color: #fca5a5;
        }
    </style>
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Animated background -->
    <div class="bg-grid"></div>
    <div class="glow-blob blob-1"></div>
    <div class="glow-blob blob-2"></div>
    <div class="glow-blob blob-3"></div>

    <!-- Navigation Bar -->
    <nav class="nav-bar">
        <div class="nav-logo">C-TOKEN CSM++</div>
        <div style="display: flex; gap: 2rem; align-items: center;">
            <a href="#features" style="color: var(--color-text-secondary); hover: color: var(--color-primary);">Features</a>
            <a href="#benchmark" style="color: var(--color-text-secondary);">Benchmark</a>
            <a href="#demo" style="color: var(--color-text-secondary);">Demo</a>
            <button class="btn btn-primary" style="padding: 0.6rem 1.3rem;">Get Started</button>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <style>
        .bg-grid {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background-image: 
                linear-gradient(rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.1) 1px, transparent 1px),
                linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.1) 1px, transparent 1px);
            background-size: 60px 60px;
            pointer-events: none;
            z-index: 0;
        }

        .glow-blob {
            position: absolute;
            border-radius: 50%;
            filter: blur(80px);
            opacity: 0.3;
            animation: float 8s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        .blob-1 {
            width: 300px;
            height: 300px;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, #3b82f6, rgba(59, 130, 246, 0));
            top: 10%;
            left: 5%;
            animation-delay: 0s;
        }

        .blob-2 {
            width: 250px;
            height: 250px;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, #a855f7, rgba(168, 85, 247, 0));
            top: 50%;
            right: 10%;
            animation-delay: 2s;
        }

        .blob-3 {
            width: 280px;
            height: 280px;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, #ec4899, rgba(236, 72, 153, 0));
            bottom: 10%;
            left: 20%;
            animation-delay: 4s;
        }
    </style>

    <div class="content-wrapper">
        <!-- HERO SECTION - Enhanced -->
        <section id="hero" class="section-padding min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center relative" style="padding-top: 8rem;">
            <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto text-center px-4">
                <!-- Badge -->
                <div class="mb-8 fade-in-up" style="animation-delay: 0s;">
                    <span class="badge">
                        <span>⚡</span>
                        <span>Production-Ready Semantic Compression Engine</span>
                    </span>
                </div>

                <!-- Main Headline -->
                <h1 class="hero-text gradient-text mb-6 fade-in-up" style="animation-delay: 0.1s;">
                    Compression Meets<br>Intelligence
                </h1>

                <!-- Subheading -->
                <p class="subtitle-text text-gray-400 mb-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto fade-in-up" style="animation-delay: 0.2s;">
                    C-TOKEN CSM++ — The first entropy-based semantic compression layer for enterprise AI pipelines. 
                    <span class="text-blue-300">18x compression on logs</span>, 
                    <span class="text-purple-300">automatic ML features</span>, and 
                    <span class="text-pink-300">deterministic output</span> guaranteed.
                </p>

                <!-- Key Metrics -->
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto fade-in-up" style="animation-delay: 0.3s;">
                    <div class="stat-box">
                        <div class="stat-value">50K+</div>
                        <div class="stat-label">Tokens/Second</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-box">
                        <div class="stat-value">&lt;5ms</div>
                        <div class="stat-label">Latency</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-box">
                        <div class="stat-value">18x</div>
                        <div class="stat-label">Compression</div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- CTA Buttons -->
                <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center mb-12 fade-in-up" style="animation-delay: 0.4s;">
                    <button onclick="document.getElementById('demo').scrollIntoView({ behavior: 'smooth' })" class="btn btn-primary" style="padding: 1rem 2rem; font-size: 1rem;">
                        Try Live Demo →
                    </button>
                    <button class="btn btn-secondary" style="padding: 1rem 2rem; font-size: 1rem;">
                        View Documentation
                    </button>
                </div>

                <!-- Trust indicators -->
                <div class="flex justify-center gap-4 fade-in-up" style="animation-delay: 0.5s;">
                    <div class="text-sm text-gray-500">✓ Battle-tested at scale</div>
                    <div class="text-sm text-gray-500">✓ Deterministic</div>
                    <div class="text-sm text-gray-500">✓ Open Spec</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- TRUST BADGES - Enhanced -->
        <section class="section-padding" style="margin-top: 2rem;">
            <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
                <p class="text-center text-gray-500 text-sm mb-10 uppercase tracking-wider font-semibold">Trusted by Enterprise Teams</p>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
                    <div class="glass rounded-lg p-6 text-center feature-card">
                        <div class="text-3xl mb-3">🔐</div>
                        <h4 class="font-bold text-white mb-2">Deterministic</h4>
                        <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Same input = identical output</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="glass rounded-lg p-6 text-center feature-card">
                        <div class="text-3xl mb-3">🧠</div>
                        <h4 class="font-bold text-white mb-2">Semantic-Aware</h4>
                        <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Context-preserving compression</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="glass rounded-lg p-6 text-center feature-card">
                        <div class="text-3xl mb-3">✅</div>
                        <h4 class="font-bold text-white mb-2">Production Ready</h4>
                        <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Battle-tested at scale</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="glass rounded-lg p-6 text-center feature-card">
                        <div class="text-3xl mb-3">⚡</div>
                        <h4 class="font-bold text-white mb-2">AI Optimized</h4>
                        <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Built for LLM pipelines</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- DOMAIN-SPECIFIC USE CASES -->
        <section class="section-padding max-w-5xl mx-auto border-t border-gray-700/50">
            <div class="text-center mb-12">
                <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold gradient-text mb-4">Purpose-Built for Three Domains</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-400">Not a general-purpose compressor. Domain-aware algorithms for maximum impact.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
                <!-- Domain 1: Logs -->
                <div class="glass rounded-xl p-8 feature-card">
                    <div class="text-4xl mb-4">📊</div>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-blue-400">Application Logs</h3>
                    <div class="space-y-3 text-gray-300">
                        <div>
                            <div class="font-semibold text-sm">Compression Ratio</div>
                            <div class="text-xl font-bold text-blue-400">8x – 20x</div>
                            <div class="text-xs text-gray-500">vs gzip 2.3x better</div>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <div class="font-semibold text-sm text-white">Use Case</div>
                            <p class="text-sm">Server logs, K8s events, audit logs, app errors. Highly repetitive (80-95% template overlap).</p>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <div class="font-semibold text-sm text-white">Output</div>
                            <p class="text-sm">Pattern ID, template, extracted slots (IP, timestamp, error code), anomaly score.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Domain 2: Code -->
                <div class="glass rounded-xl p-8 feature-card">
                    <div class="text-4xl mb-4">💻</div>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-purple-400">Source Code</h3>
                    <div class="space-y-3 text-gray-300">
                        <div>
                            <div class="font-semibold text-sm">Compression Ratio</div>
                            <div class="text-xl font-bold text-purple-400">4x – 10x</div>
                            <div class="text-xs text-gray-500">vs BPE tokens</div>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <div class="font-semibold text-sm text-white">Use Case</div>
                            <p class="text-sm">GitHub repos, code review diffs, stack traces, compiler output. AST-pattern repetitive.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <div class="font-semibold text-sm text-white">Output</div>
                            <p class="text-sm">Code patterns, identifiers, complexity features, clone detection.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Domain 3: AI Training Data -->
                <div class="glass rounded-xl p-8 feature-card">
                    <div class="text-4xl mb-4">🤖</div>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-pink-400">AI Datasets</h3>
                    <div class="space-y-3 text-gray-300">
                        <div>
                            <div class="font-semibold text-sm">Compression Ratio</div>
                            <div class="text-xl font-bold text-pink-400">2x – 4x</div>
                            <div class="text-xs text-gray-500">vs BPE, with dedup</div>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <div class="font-semibold text-sm text-white">Use Case</div>
                            <p class="text-sm">Instruction datasets, QA pairs, training corpora. Slot-rich structured text.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <div class="font-semibold text-sm text-white">Output</div>
                            <p class="text-sm">Deduplicated patterns, slot-normalized features, data quality scoring.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- PROBLEM → SOLUTION → MOAT (Enhanced) -->
        <section class="section-padding max-w-5xl mx-auto">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
                <div class="fade-in-up">
                    <div class="text-5xl mb-4">❌</div>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">The Problem</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">
                        Traditional compression (gzip, zstd) is <span class="text-red-400 font-semibold">byte-level and semantically unaware</span>. Traditional tokenizers (BPE) are <span class="text-red-400 font-semibold">domain-agnostic</span>.
                    </p>
                    <ul class="text-sm text-gray-400 space-y-2">
                        <li>• Static token mappings (no adaptation)</li>
                        <li>• No semantic understanding (just pattern matching)</li>
                        <li>• Wasted capacity on structured data (logs, code)</li>
                        <li>• No ML features extracted automatically</li>
                        <li>• Output not interpretable by humans</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="fade-in-up" style="animation-delay: 0.1s;">
                    <div class="text-5xl mb-4">💡</div>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Our Solution</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">
                        <span class="text-blue-400 font-semibold">CSM++ = Compression + Feature Engineering + Anomaly Detection</span>
                    </p>
                    <ul class="text-sm text-gray-400 space-y-2">
                        <li>✓ Entropy-based adaptive token mapping</li>
                        <li>✓ Domain-aware pattern discovery (Viterbi DP)</li>
                        <li>✓ Semantic slot extraction (IP, timestamp, level...)</li>
                        <li>✓ Automatic ML feature generation</li>
                        <li>✓ Human-readable templates + anomaly scores</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="fade-in-up" style="animation-delay: 0.2s;">
                    <div class="text-5xl mb-4">🛡️</div>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">The Moat</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">
                        <span class="text-purple-400 font-semibold">Deterministic entropy-based pattern matching</span>
                    </p>
                    <ul class="text-sm text-gray-400 space-y-2">
                        <li>✓ FST (Finite State Transducer) not HashMap</li>
                        <li>✓ Viterbi DP optimal pattern selection</li>
                        <li>✓ Proprietary PPMI scoring for discovery</li>
                        <li>✓ Reproducible &amp; standardized output</li>
                        <li>✓ 3+ years patent-pending methodology</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- FEATURES GRID -->
        <section class="section-padding bg-gradient-to-b from-transparent via-purple-950/10 to-transparent border-t border-b border-purple-900/30">
            <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
                <div class="text-center mb-12">
                    <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold gradient-text mb-4">Core Architecture</h2>
                    <p class="text-gray-400">Five-layer pipeline: Ingestion → Core → Semantic → Feature Store → Output</p>
                </div>

                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                    <div class="glass rounded-xl p-8 feature-card">
                        <div class="text-3xl mb-4">🔄</div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">FST Pattern Matching</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-300">Finite State Transducer (not HashMap) for O(k) pattern lookup. 65K patterns in just 5 MB. Better cache locality than traditional hash tables.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="glass rounded-xl p-8 feature-card">
                        <div class="text-3xl mb-4">📈</div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Viterbi DP Selection</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-300">Dynamic programming finds globally optimal pattern assignments. Not greedy. Guarantees maximum compression ratio given vocabulary.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="glass rounded-xl p-8 feature-card">
                        <div class="text-3xl mb-4">🎯</div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Smart Slot Extraction</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-300">Typed slot extraction: IP addresses, timestamps, log levels, UUIDs, paths, hex values, integers, floats. Not just strings.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="glass rounded-xl p-8 feature-card">
                        <div class="text-3xl mb-4">🚀</div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Automatic Feature Engineering</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-300">Generates ML features automatically: pattern frequency (1m/1h windows), slot statistics, sequence PMI, anomaly scores.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="glass rounded-xl p-8 feature-card">
                        <div class="text-3xl mb-4">⚡</div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">SIMD + Rust Core</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-300">Pure Rust with AVX-512 vectorization. Zero-copy processing. 8-16 tokens per CPU cycle. No garbage collection.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="glass rounded-xl p-8 feature-card">
                        <div class="text-3xl mb-4">🐍</div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Python + Streaming</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-300">PyO3 bindings for seamless integration. Streaming pipeline for real-time Kafka. Also CLI tool included.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

